reviewText: Funny holiday episodes, great for the family.
My son loves Power Rangers! This just got delivered today and he has already watched every episode 3 times.
This is a good dvd. But you only get the one thing from it. The Megaforce Halloween ep. Thats it.
thank you very and have a nice day

I really liked watching this each because episode has to do this Halloween.  The episodes are: Raising Spirits" from Megaforce, "Trickster Treat" from Super Samurai, "Zedd's Monster Mash" from Mighty Morphin and "It Came From Angel Grove" from Zeo for a total of four episodes.  Anyone who likes Power Rangers will like this and is a must to add to the collection.
